		<label>Astra Militarum Bike</label>
		<description>Bikes are fast-moving ground vehicles capable of carrying up to one rider and usually mounting a light weapon. Bikes are used by several forces of the Imperium as often for reconnaissance and rapid support roles. \n\n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Crew:&lt;/color&gt; Driver x1. \n&lt;color=#bb8f04&gt;Fuel type:&lt;/color&gt; Chemfuel</description>
